@baseUrl = http://localhost:5002
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@token =

### 获取 CSRF Token
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 查询我的代理配置
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 创建代理配置（成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentUserId": 1002,
  "startTime": "2026-03-02T08:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-03-31T18:00:00Z"
}

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentUserId": 1002,
  "startTime": "2026-03-02T08:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-03-31T18:00:00Z"
}

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentUserId": 1002,
  "startTime": "2026-03-02T08:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-03-31T18:00:00Z"
}

### 安全负例：幂等冲突（同 key 不同 payload，第二次应返回 409）
@idemConflictAgent = approval-agent-conflict-001
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentUserId": 1002,
  "startTime": "2026-03-02T08:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-03-31T18:00:00Z"
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "agentUserId": 1003,
  "startTime": "2026-03-02T08:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-03-31T18:00:00Z"
}

### 删除代理配置（成功）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/agents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
